{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were shops, but everything was homemade and preserved for the winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's how-- that was always very exciting that the women-- everything was exciting because as a child, everything gets exciting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And also nothing was happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was-- I remember the first picture house came to town because we weren't allowed to go because [INAUDIBLE] people just don't go to pictures.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we used to look through the keyhole and do all sorts of things just to get a glimpse of this black and white silent films.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I always think-- I always remember the Shirley Temple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And so anything like that, like the corn harvest-- we used to have people specially employed for the corn harvest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then there was a big urn in the garden, and all the corn was put in there with the fresh ones.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you eat at corn all day long, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the same with other things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "These women came for-- five women-- and they boiled the tomatoes in huge, big urns and then sift them into bottles and preserve them for over the winter.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then the strawberries were ready.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were picked and so that was always for us children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, it was always the event.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this event happened all summer-- spring and summer, winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we just enjoyed all the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all the things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did-- we did have our-- everybody had their own little garden near the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very encouraged to grow things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, I had a little vegetable patch and a little-- the fruit trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to sit-- climb on the fruit trees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it-- it was a real country life, which is such a shame.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's missing these days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was really, very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
